This guide will help you set up a production domain. The production domain is the domain of your production Instance, your live site available to visitors.

## Requirements
To be able to set up a production domain on the Partner Portal, you have to [Create the Domain as a DNS Zone](/developer-guide/partner-portal/domains/dns-setting-up-production-domain) first.

